            JazzUp Salon, we believe in helping you express your unique style, making us the perfect
            place to try something new.
          </div>
          <a href={getPathPrefix('/theme/5/contact-us')} class="btn btn-lg btn-primary"
            >Contact Us</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
